      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_7704253926008301605.png",
                "id": "talent85147",
                "key": "Abductive Reasoning",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Abductive Reasoning"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chisel-Light Mirror</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Chisel-Light Mirror</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt by the character is converted to <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After this character performs a Normal Attack:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span>. If it is a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Charged Attack</span>, this state's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> +1.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span>: 2 (Can stack. Max 3 Rounds.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/8491b6dd997a8a4878767f1191a2b6aa_5628321749148527952.png",
                "id": "talent26434",
                "key": "Universality: An Elaboration on Form",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Universality: An Elaboration on Form"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, consumes <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chisel-Light Mirror</span>, with the DMG bonus based on <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chisel-Light Mirror</span>'s <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds)</span> consumed.<br>If <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chisel-Light Mirror Duration (Rounds)</span> consumed is 0/1/2, then apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Chisel-Light Mirror </span>with 3/2/1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> to this character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Chisel-Light Mirror</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt by the character is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After this character performs a Normal Attack:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. If it is a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Charged Attack</span>, this state's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> +1.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span>: 2 (Can stack. Max 3 Rounds.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/a3b3108e0046cb101533a3bf6dcbe717_8692637226440152587.png",
                "id": "talent82339",
                "key": "Particular Field: Fetters of Phenomena",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Particular Field: Fetters of Phenomena"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_202639486180190917.png",
                "id": "talent16408",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Charged Attack</span></strong><br>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong><br>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5829597877060577948.png",
                "id": "talent84373",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
